1，安装mysql，可以用navicat 辅助，然后创建一个表格。并且往表格中插入三条数据。
```
/*
Navicat MySQL Data Transfer

Source Server         : remote-100.106.43.30
Source Server Version : 50518
Source Host           : 100.106.43.30:3306
Source Database       : test

Target Server Type    : MYSQL
Target Server Version : 50518
File Encoding         : 65001

Date: 2016-12-24 15:17:43
*/

SET FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS=0;

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for user
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `user`;
CREATE TABLE `user` (
  `id` int(10) NOT NULL,
  `username` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `password` varchar(20) NOT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

-- ----------------------------
-- Records of user
-- ----------------------------
INSERT INTO `user` VALUES ('1', 'xiaohong', '123456');
INSERT INTO `user` VALUES ('2', 'xiaohua', '123456');
INSERT INTO `user` VALUES ('3', 'xiaoniao', '123456');
```


2，建立一个maven 工程，pom文件修改如下：
<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
  xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd">
  <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>

  <groupId>com.sydney.dream</groupId>
  <artifactId>FirstApp</artifactId>
  <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
  <packaging>jar</packaging>

  <name>FirstApp</name>
  <url>http://maven.apache.org</url>

  <properties>
    <project.build.sourceEncoding>UTF-8</project.build.sourceEncoding>
    <mysql-connector-java.version>5.1.25</mysql-connector-java.version>
    <mybatis.version>3.2.7</mybatis.version>
    <junit.version>3.8.1</junit.version>
  </properties>

  <dependencies>
    <dependency>
      <groupId>junit</groupId>
      <artifactId>junit</artifactId>
      <version>${junit.version}</version>
      <scope>test</scope>
    </dependency>
    <dependency>
      <groupId>org.mybatis</groupId>
      <artifactId>mybatis</artifactId>
      <version>${mybatis.version}</version>
    </dependency>
    <dependency>
      <groupId>mysql</groupId>
      <artifactId>mysql-connector-java</artifactId>
      <version>${mysql-connector-java.version}</version>
    </dependency>
  </dependencies>
  <repositories>
    <repository>
      <id>nexus</id>
      <name>Team Nexus Repository</name>
      <url>http://192.168.74.131:8081/nexus/content/groups/MyRepositories/</url>
    </repository>
  </repositories>
  <build>
    <resources>
      <resource>
        <directory>src/main/java</directory>
        <includes>
          <include>**/*.xml</include>
        </includes>
        <filtering>true</filtering>
      </resource>
    </resources>
  </build>
</project>

3，目录结构大致如下：
项目目录结构如下
FirstApp
-----src
--------main
------------java
----------------com.sydney.dream
--------------------------------model
-------------------------------------mapper
-------------------------------------------IUserOperationMapper.xml
-------------------------------------------UserMapper.xml
-------------------------------------User.java
-------------------------------------Articale.java
--------------------------------Interface
-----------------------------------------IUserOperation.java
--------------------------------Main.java
------------resources
---------------------db.properties
---------------------mybaties-config.xml
--------test
------------com.sydney.dream
----------------------------MainTest.java
--------pom.xml
